title: Find high value contracts in the public sector

heading_context: Find high value contracts in the public sector
chunks.html_content:
Use the Find a Tender service to search and apply for high value contracts in the UK’s public and utilities sectors. High value contracts are usually above £138,760, including VAT.

Find a Tender replaced the EU’s Tenders Electronic Daily for high value contracts in the UK on 1 January 2021.
